title: LeSean McCoy trade reaction
itunes:title: LeSean McCoy trade reaction
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the LeSean McCoy-Kiko Alonso trade and what it means for the Eagles and Bills. Plus, more reaction to Peyton Manning's reported new contract, the Matt Cassel trade and free agency team needs.
